task.summary: Added autoFill and nextId to functionalities
Added readAll to find soft-deleted object
Added token verification, invalidating tokens, logout, encrypting power and roles into jwt
Added '/editRoles' to add and remove roles from users
Added canActivate RouteGuard, loading roles, fetch power from JWT
Added AuthService for RouteGuard, decodes JWT cookie and loads roles
Now deleting cookie on logout, moved cookie name to variable
Switched to primeng's sidebar and menu
Separated verifyUser() and verifyUserLight() for different security levels and higher performance
Added home-button, icons and changed calls to AuthService
Added /userDetails/:userId for getting info about a specific user
Added error code for invalid REST params
Separated AuthLoginWrapper and AuthLogin, added styling to AuthLogin
Created AuthLoginWrapper for displaying 'already logged in' and using AuthLogin in a dialog
Added DialogWrapper and DialogModule to dynamically display data
Changed layout; added user detail button; moved login/logout to sidebar menu
Return invalid credentials error if user doesn't exist
Added ErrorHandlingService; functionality for display errors returned over http
